item.title: CVE-2019-17338|2024-09-17T01:36:54.758Z -- tibco%20software%20inc. -- tibco%20patterns%20-%20search
item.description: The user interface component of TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO Patterns - Search contains multiple vulnerabilities that theoretically allow authenticated users to perform persistent cross-site scripting (XSS) attacks. Affected releases are TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO Patterns - Search: versions 5.4.0 and below.
